WEBVTT

01:38.160 --> 01:40.480
EPISODE 25

01:42.720 --> 01:46.280
Hello, Weiwei? What's wrong, Weiwei?

01:47.040 --> 01:50.440
Nothing. I have to go.

01:53.360 --> 01:54.200
Hello?

02:17.040 --> 02:18.400
Let's leave early today.

02:18.800 --> 02:20.480
Move your stuff to my apartment,

02:20.800 --> 02:22.480
and I'll move to my parents' place.

02:23.520 --> 02:24.360
I can do it myself.

02:26.200 --> 02:27.040
Are you sure?

02:29.280 --> 02:30.480
Absolutely.

04:31.040 --> 04:32.680
They do live together.

04:41.200 --> 04:44.480
We meet again, Luwei Weiwei.

04:47.800 --> 04:48.640
Zhenshui Wuxiang?

04:50.040 --> 04:53.320
That's my handle.
My name is Zhen Shaoxiang.

04:53.760 --> 04:54.920
You can call me Shaoxiang.

04:58.480 --> 05:00.120
Where are you going? I'll give you a ride.

05:01.880 --> 05:03.800
It's okay. I can go by myself.

05:05.120 --> 05:08.680
It's all right.
We had some misunderstanding in the game,

05:08.760 --> 05:10.720
but I think we're still friends.

05:11.920 --> 05:15.040
It's not about the game.
I just hate to trouble others.

05:15.120 --> 05:16.080
Thank you.

05:25.520 --> 05:28.040
All right, I won't insist.

05:29.040 --> 05:30.960
By the way, what's your real name?

05:31.040 --> 05:33.880
I can't call you Luwei Weiwei
next time I see you.

05:33.960 --> 05:34.880
That's so out of character.

05:35.840 --> 05:37.440
I don't think we'll meet again.

05:38.960 --> 05:40.480
I do.

05:41.640 --> 05:45.400
The thing is, Zhao Erxi already told me
your real name.

05:45.880 --> 05:48.400
How else would I know you live here?

05:50.960 --> 05:53.000
She told you my surname is Lu?

05:53.920 --> 05:55.520
So, your surname is Lu.

05:56.640 --> 05:57.480
Of course.

06:06.680 --> 06:08.280
Why are you laughing?

06:09.280 --> 06:12.560
Let me give you a ride.
It'll take you forever by foot.

06:13.640 --> 06:16.320
It's okay. I'm going to my boyfriend's.

06:16.560 --> 06:18.560
It's not appropriate to ride with you.

06:20.640 --> 06:22.760
Your boyfriend? Xiao Nai?

06:27.280 --> 06:30.040
He came to my office
to ask for investment,

06:30.240 --> 06:32.600
but they're an immature student team.

06:40.160 --> 06:41.920
If I remember correctly,

06:42.000 --> 06:44.000
your company is Zhenyi Tech?

06:47.720 --> 06:51.200
Mr. Zhen, on the company level,

06:51.360 --> 06:52.600
Zhiyi and Zhenyi

06:52.680 --> 06:54.960
are competing for the right to develop
"A New Chinese Ghost Story."

06:55.880 --> 06:57.880
That proves the two companies
are of the same caliber.

06:58.880 --> 07:00.360
On the personal level,

07:00.840 --> 07:04.680
my boyfriend is the head programmer
and head strategist of Zhiyi Tech.

07:05.320 --> 07:08.480
I wonder what function
you serve in Zhenyi.

07:12.480 --> 07:14.320
On behalf of my boyfriend,

07:14.560 --> 07:16.280
I thank you
for withholding the investment.

07:47.040 --> 07:49.640
The exact same attitude as in the game.

07:50.240 --> 07:51.400
Interesting.

08:32.880 --> 08:35.919
I emptied half the closet for you.
Help yourself.

08:38.320 --> 08:40.240
I'll settle in when you're done.

08:47.400 --> 08:50.440
Are you really going to give me your room?

08:52.000 --> 08:54.800
I have no confidence in my self-control.

08:56.680 --> 08:58.680
Thankfully I can stay
at my parents' place,

08:59.080 --> 09:00.680
otherwise I'd have to sleep
in the office.

09:49.080 --> 09:50.240
Help me clean up.

09:53.960 --> 09:55.120
I'll get a mop.

10:08.560 --> 10:10.960
Okay. Thanks. I got it.

10:13.520 --> 10:15.040
The plumber will be here tomorrow.

10:17.440 --> 10:18.560
I'm so glad these boxes are okay.

10:19.280 --> 10:22.440
Otherwise, your Professor Xiao would cry
for three days.

10:23.920 --> 10:25.680
I think Professor Xiao would cry
for three days,

10:25.760 --> 10:27.480
because you speak of him like that.

10:32.760 --> 10:34.320
What do we do with these?

10:35.480 --> 10:37.760
Pack them up and put them in my place.

10:39.240 --> 10:41.960
Put the handwritten manuscripts in a bag.

10:42.440 --> 10:43.280
Okay.

10:48.320 --> 10:50.960
Don't worry. Your Wu Guanzhongs are fine.

10:51.040 --> 10:55.320
So are your Xu Beihongs.
Yes, they've all been put away.

10:55.840 --> 10:58.760
I'll keep them at my place off-campus.
Okay.

11:01.080 --> 11:03.560
Where do we put these?

11:07.360 --> 11:10.400
Put them in the closet for now,
since there's nowhere else.

11:13.640 --> 11:17.480
You said, you'd sleep in the office,

11:17.560 --> 11:19.200
if you couldn't stay at
your parents' place.

11:20.080 --> 11:22.440
So, where will you stay tonight?

11:23.560 --> 11:25.480
I don't mind sleeping in the office,

11:25.560 --> 11:28.440
but these paintings
are my parents' precious collections.

11:28.720 --> 11:30.000
I can't let anything happen to them.

11:30.640 --> 11:32.560
I'm worried with you here alone.

11:33.720 --> 11:36.920
- So?
- I'll stay and keep an eye on them.

12:04.440 --> 12:09.280
This could be the two of us
several decades from now. I like it.

12:40.920 --> 12:41.960
Here's the update!

12:42.040 --> 12:45.720
Today, Coffee's eating regularly
and pooping regularly.

12:45.800 --> 12:49.040
He's just a bit sluggish.
He keeps gazing out of the window,

12:49.120 --> 12:51.080
probably missing you.

12:55.920 --> 12:59.320
I have successfully won Coffee over.

12:59.400 --> 13:01.120
We're now besties forever.

13:04.280 --> 13:05.640
Coffee's off-screen line is,

13:05.840 --> 13:09.400
"Dissing Ms. Erxi is dissing me.

13:09.480 --> 13:12.080
I sneer at you!"

13:22.200 --> 13:25.000
Are you still mad at me?

13:26.000 --> 13:28.600
It was my bad.

13:29.560 --> 13:32.080
I'll wait for you
at the same place in the game.

13:34.800 --> 13:38.080
I'll let you kill me a hundred times.
Will that do?

14:12.440 --> 14:14.960
Are you still mad at me?

14:16.280 --> 14:18.840
It was my bad.

14:19.880 --> 14:22.280
I'll wait for you
at the same place in the game.

14:25.200 --> 14:28.280
I'll let you kill me a hundred times.
Will that do?

15:03.400 --> 15:05.120
Coffee...

15:05.640 --> 15:08.440
your poop-scooper
has shut us out for real.

15:10.120 --> 15:11.920
Women are so troublesome.

15:14.880 --> 15:15.880
Oh, yeah!

15:17.560 --> 15:20.680
I still have a score to settle.
I nearly forgot.

15:26.160 --> 15:31.160
Yiran, did you delete the video
on my phone?

15:31.440 --> 15:33.000
No. Why?

15:33.600 --> 15:34.680
That's odd.

15:34.760 --> 15:37.000
How did the video on my phone just vanish?

15:38.040 --> 15:40.920
By the way, how did Xiao Nai react
to the video?

15:41.640 --> 15:44.160
- I don't know.
- You don't?

15:44.240 --> 15:47.200
No. He asked me where it was shot.

15:47.280 --> 15:50.280
When was it shot? I told him everything.

15:50.360 --> 15:52.800
Then he made me delete the video
on my phone.

15:53.520 --> 15:55.920
- That's it?
- Yes, that's it.

15:56.440 --> 15:59.080
What does he think about it now?

15:59.160 --> 16:01.320
Has he seen through
Bei Weiwei's pretense?

16:02.080 --> 16:05.080
Wait, now we don't have a copy
of the video anymore.

16:06.520 --> 16:08.720
He's seen it already.
I'm sure he'll get it.

16:10.160 --> 16:12.640
They might be breaking up, as we speak.

16:17.960 --> 16:21.840
Why is Cao Guang calling me?

16:24.760 --> 16:26.880
Hello? What do you want, Cao Guang?

16:27.440 --> 16:28.480
Tomorrow morning at ten,

16:28.560 --> 16:30.960
come to the school south gate
with Meng Yiran.

16:31.520 --> 16:32.920
What's this attitude?

16:33.000 --> 16:35.320
You think you can summon us?
Who do you think you are?

16:35.480 --> 16:38.760
You secretly filmed me, spread the video,
and smeared a fellow student's name.

16:38.840 --> 16:39.800
What do you think that makes you?

16:40.920 --> 16:42.680
If I don't see you two tomorrow morning,

16:42.760 --> 16:43.960
you'll suffer the consequences.

16:46.200 --> 16:49.600
Hey! Hello? Hello?

17:03.080 --> 17:05.280
What do we do now, Yiran?

17:05.720 --> 17:08.520
I hear Cao Guang's family is powerful.

17:09.240 --> 17:11.599
Is he going to get back at us?

17:12.440 --> 17:15.119
It was wrong of you to secretly film him,

17:15.520 --> 17:17.359
but your intention wasn't bad.

17:17.720 --> 17:21.280
If he's reasonable,
he won't give you a hard time.

17:22.400 --> 17:25.880
How did Cao Guang find out
it was me who shot the video?

17:27.119 --> 17:28.880
Did Xiao Nai tell him?

17:30.920 --> 17:34.040
That's right! Why didn't I think of it?

17:34.560 --> 17:37.080
Xiao Nai must have confirmed it
with Cao Guang.

17:37.840 --> 17:39.680
Nana, he believes me!

17:40.520 --> 17:42.760
It's hard evidence.
Why wouldn't he believe you?

17:44.560 --> 17:47.320
I wonder what kind of spell
Bei Weiwei has them under.

17:47.680 --> 17:50.800
I can't believe I only thought of it now.
I'm so stupid.

17:54.640 --> 17:58.560
Is Cao Guang demanding to meet with us,
because he's humiliated?

18:00.120 --> 18:03.680
He's been duped by a girl,
and his love rival confronted him.

18:05.120 --> 18:07.600
He must be utterly humiliated.

18:09.440 --> 18:11.160
I guess so.

18:11.480 --> 18:14.040
It's okay. When he gets here,

18:14.280 --> 18:16.480
you just apologize to him.
It should be fine.

18:27.360 --> 18:31.960
Cao Guang, you asked to meet with us,
yet you're late.

18:32.040 --> 18:34.440
You made us wait under the scorching sun.

18:34.520 --> 18:35.920
You're so mean!

18:42.680 --> 18:44.960
You should know I'm here
to settle the score, right?

18:45.040 --> 18:46.480
Don't use that tone with me.

18:49.920 --> 18:52.360
That's how I always talk.

18:53.400 --> 18:56.000
It was wrong of me to film you secretly,

18:56.640 --> 18:59.000
but I didn't do it on purpose.

18:59.080 --> 19:00.840
It was happenstance.

19:01.720 --> 19:04.160
Fine. I apologize, okay?

19:04.360 --> 19:07.240
Please be the bigger person
and forgive me.

19:10.200 --> 19:13.720
Cao Guang, what Nana did was wrong,

19:13.840 --> 19:15.680
but her intention was good.

19:15.920 --> 19:19.160
She just didn't want you and Xiao Nai
to be duped.

19:21.320 --> 19:23.560
Meng Yiran,
you're into Xiao Nai, right?

19:26.960 --> 19:29.560
You want to steal Xiao Nai
from Bei Weiwei.

19:30.680 --> 19:33.080
It has nothing to do with my feelings.

19:33.320 --> 19:36.280
I just don't want to see
you guys be duped.

19:37.000 --> 19:39.240
Quit making self-aggrandizing excuses.

19:39.320 --> 19:41.680
You know perfectly well
why you're doing this.

19:43.120 --> 19:46.040
And, no matter how hard you try,

19:46.120 --> 19:48.440
Xiao Nai would never fall for
a stupid person like you.

19:49.600 --> 19:51.040
Is this how you talk to a girl?

19:51.480 --> 19:53.320
You should be so glad you're girls.

19:53.400 --> 19:55.480
Why else would I
let you off the hook so easily?

19:58.440 --> 20:02.040
End this now, Nana, and I'll let it go.

20:05.240 --> 20:07.680
I'm warning you, watch your mouths.

20:08.360 --> 20:11.840
If I hear any more hurtful rumors
about Bei Weiwei,

20:11.920 --> 20:14.920
I'll make you pay,
even if they don't come from you.

20:15.560 --> 20:17.600
So, it's still about Bei Weiwei!

20:18.360 --> 20:20.400
I'm surprised a genius like you

20:20.480 --> 20:22.200
would be such a fool in lust.

20:24.160 --> 20:26.680
Who knew you'd continue to defend the name

20:26.760 --> 20:27.720
of a two-timing girl?

20:28.160 --> 20:29.720
Didn't you hear what I just said?

20:31.560 --> 20:34.920
You were the one who said
she's a two-timer, not me.

20:35.440 --> 20:36.400
It's a case of mistaken identity.

20:38.000 --> 20:38.840
Mistaken identity?

20:40.880 --> 20:44.080
It wasn't Bei Weiwei? Who was it then?

20:44.720 --> 20:46.200
It has nothing to do with you.

20:50.520 --> 20:53.560
Just remember, watch your mouths.

20:53.960 --> 20:56.600
- Otherwise, you'll get it.
- Hey...

20:56.760 --> 20:57.800
You've been warned.

21:01.960 --> 21:04.840
Also, you can court guys,

21:07.240 --> 21:09.080
but using those dirty tricks

21:09.160 --> 21:10.800
makes you crass, don't you think?

22:15.720 --> 22:17.680
You're not going to work this afternoon?

22:17.800 --> 22:19.200
Our progress is good.

22:19.360 --> 22:21.120
So, no more working overtime.

22:22.520 --> 22:23.920
Are you shooing me away?

22:25.200 --> 22:26.520
Why would I do that?

22:26.600 --> 22:28.920
I just don't want to distract you
from your your work.

22:30.760 --> 22:33.800
Get your laptop and sit down next to me.

22:34.880 --> 22:35.720
Okay.

23:41.720 --> 23:44.320
I'm surprised to see you again.

23:57.840 --> 24:00.120
Do you remember this place, Luwei?

24:00.680 --> 24:03.240
I think this is where
we first took on an outdoor boss,

24:03.920 --> 24:05.560
after we became an in-game couple.

24:06.040 --> 24:09.200
We were outnumbered
and likely to be annihilated.

24:09.600 --> 24:12.640
You exploded in the end
and saved our team.

24:13.120 --> 24:16.360
You werealways charging ahead,
when we went to an instance dungeon.

24:16.880 --> 24:18.800
You never needed any looking-after.

24:19.040 --> 24:22.160
I do miss the time
when we fought side by side.

24:23.320 --> 24:26.000
Thinking back on it now,

24:26.400 --> 24:28.360
you've were always my best partner.

24:30.400 --> 24:32.720
If I don't say these things in the game,

24:33.320 --> 24:36.680
I'd never be able to tell you in person.

24:52.480 --> 24:56.600
Weiwei? Are you there?
Did you get kicked offline?

25:11.840 --> 25:15.840
Luwei Weiwei,
I took what we had for granted.

25:16.880 --> 25:19.440
After all this, I finally realized

25:19.520 --> 25:22.400
what kind of a girl is best for me.

25:22.480 --> 25:26.920
People make mistakes.
I've made my share, too.

25:27.560 --> 25:31.200
If possible,
I wish none of it ever happened,

25:32.440 --> 25:34.520
but it's not too late now.

25:44.040 --> 25:47.640
Will you give me a chance to start over?
Please?

25:58.080 --> 26:03.200
I am Yixiao Naihe.

26:46.960 --> 26:48.320
What's going on?

26:50.680 --> 26:53.600
Chasing nostalgia.

26:58.440 --> 27:01.520
Zhenshui Wuxiang must be fuming now.

27:02.440 --> 27:03.880
You ran into him yesterday?

27:05.120 --> 27:06.120
I did.

27:06.360 --> 27:09.320
He somehow got the address out of Erxi.

27:09.400 --> 27:13.320
He was waiting for me outside
and lied that he knew my name.

27:13.960 --> 27:17.320
I know Erxi well.
However mad she may be at me,

27:17.400 --> 27:18.760
she'd never sell me out.

27:19.520 --> 27:23.080
So I asked him a trick question,
and his game was up.

27:27.360 --> 27:28.400
Why didn't you tell me?

27:29.760 --> 27:31.720
I forgot, since I resolved it too easily.

27:34.560 --> 27:36.960
The missus has indeed been asked out
all her life.

27:39.360 --> 27:40.640
You should tell me anyway.

27:45.000 --> 27:48.160
For the sake of fairness,
you should do the same.

27:51.920 --> 27:54.320
It is rather easy to forget. Never-mind.

27:57.880 --> 27:59.200
Why do I somehow feel like,

27:59.280 --> 28:03.160
I'm what they called
a beauty who brings disaster?

28:03.520 --> 28:05.000
I have the worst luck with men.

28:07.240 --> 28:10.560
Yes, thankfully I took you in.

28:28.040 --> 28:31.600
So, Yixiao Naihe is Xiao Nai.

28:32.480 --> 28:38.080
So what, if he's the head programmer
and head strategist of Zhiyi Tech?

28:38.840 --> 28:42.200
To me, he's nothing!

29:04.200 --> 29:07.080
Did you read the documents I gave you?

29:08.120 --> 29:12.560
You should know, we can sue your friend
with those documents.

29:13.080 --> 29:15.720
Your friend's future
will be completely destroyed.

29:16.400 --> 29:18.440
There may be prison time, too.

29:18.880 --> 29:19.920
What do you want?

29:23.880 --> 29:25.920
If you work with us,

29:26.000 --> 29:28.040
get us what we want,

29:28.120 --> 29:29.640
we can decide not to go to court.

29:31.880 --> 29:33.320
You think too highly of me.

29:33.920 --> 29:35.800
All of Xiao Nai's core code

29:35.880 --> 29:39.320
is secured
with a 128-digit encryption key.

29:39.400 --> 29:41.400
I would never be able to crack it.

29:46.600 --> 29:48.920
If you can provide other information,

29:49.000 --> 29:50.480
we'll gladly take it.

29:58.440 --> 30:01.400
How can you guarantee
Zhenyi won't press charges?

30:02.560 --> 30:05.920
Aside from this,
you have no other options.

30:15.280 --> 30:16.120
Fine.

30:19.760 --> 30:23.240
But, even if I tell you this,
you'd still have no chance.

30:28.000 --> 30:29.560
Where there is a will, there is a way.

30:59.480 --> 31:01.640
How's the situation with Zhiyi?

31:02.440 --> 31:05.920
The guy said, there is a critical flaw
with Zhiyi's game.

31:06.000 --> 31:08.800
It takes up too much RAM,
when the game is running,

31:09.280 --> 31:11.560
but Xiao Nai is working
on an optimization tool.

31:11.640 --> 31:14.040
Once it's done and applied to the game,

31:14.120 --> 31:16.160
it can drastically reduce
the RAM taken up.

31:18.680 --> 31:19.640
Can he do it?

31:20.840 --> 31:22.600
It's likely.

31:22.720 --> 31:24.720
It'll be done by September 15.

31:27.920 --> 31:32.080
Well... We can't let them succeed.

31:33.440 --> 31:37.080
But our guy isn't in a key position.

31:38.920 --> 31:40.360
He can't do much sabotage.

31:40.440 --> 31:42.600
It's a dead-end with Zhiyi.

31:44.720 --> 31:47.720
What if Fengteng moves up the demo date?

31:50.240 --> 31:53.200
That's right. Our demo is already done.

31:53.280 --> 31:55.680
- I'll see what I can do, Mr. Zhen.
- Okay.

31:57.080 --> 31:58.120
Hi, Mr. Zhen.

31:58.720 --> 32:01.600
Dad, are we competing for the right
to develop "A New Chinese Ghost Story"?

32:03.440 --> 32:04.600
You can go.

32:08.600 --> 32:10.800
It's the weekend.

32:11.000 --> 32:13.520
What brings Young Master Zhen
to the office?

32:14.040 --> 32:16.120
Dad, I'm serious.

32:16.200 --> 32:18.720
Are we competing for the right to develop
"A New Chinese Ghost Story"?

32:19.040 --> 32:20.960
How long have you worked here?

32:21.040 --> 32:23.280
You've only become curious now?

32:23.840 --> 32:25.120
I have a question for you.

32:25.200 --> 32:29.400
When will you finally settle down
and help me manage the company?

32:29.600 --> 32:30.720
Now's the time!

32:31.360 --> 32:33.160
Dad, I want to be onboard.

32:33.480 --> 32:35.720
I promise, I'll beat Zhiyi Tech,

32:35.800 --> 32:36.920
and get the project.

32:37.280 --> 32:40.040
You? Don't make trouble for me.

32:40.920 --> 32:43.840
Why would you say that, Dad?

32:43.960 --> 32:46.040
I've played "A Chinese Ghost Story"
since the beginning.

32:46.680 --> 32:50.040
Who else here
knows more about this game than me?

32:50.840 --> 32:52.920
I must join the team.

32:53.000 --> 32:54.840
I have to crush Xiao Nai.

32:56.680 --> 32:59.520
- Are you serious?
- I couldn't be more serious, Dad.

33:03.280 --> 33:08.720
Good, my son has finally grown up.

33:44.120 --> 33:46.720
We paid you so much money,

33:46.800 --> 33:48.600
and this is what you produce?

33:51.920 --> 33:56.240
Mr. Zhen,
how would you like us to improve?

33:58.160 --> 34:00.560
Have you ever played
"A Chinese Ghost Story"?

34:04.280 --> 34:05.120
Yes.

34:05.560 --> 34:08.080
- For how long?
- Mostly more than a year.

34:10.760 --> 34:12.719
How have you played it?

34:13.400 --> 34:15.480
You log in every day, for a few minutes?

34:19.800 --> 34:22.199
As a seasoned player
of "A Chinese Ghost Story,"

34:22.280 --> 34:23.520
I'm telling you,

34:23.800 --> 34:26.880
your demo has no draw for me whatsoever,

34:27.120 --> 34:29.280
not to mention attracting new players.

34:31.960 --> 34:35.120
The character design is mediocre.
The skill sets are ambiguous.

34:35.199 --> 34:37.000
The scenes are crude.

34:37.880 --> 34:40.480
I don't see any creativity.

34:40.960 --> 34:43.639
What would you like to do, Mr. Zhen?

34:44.639 --> 34:46.840
I've played this game for years.

34:46.920 --> 34:49.080
I have my own observations and ideas.

34:49.600 --> 34:51.000
Make changes based on my feedback.

34:54.520 --> 34:56.600
Mr. Zhen, the demo is in a month.

34:56.679 --> 34:59.400
If we make changes now,
we could run out of time.

34:59.720 --> 35:01.720
I don't want to hear it.

35:02.600 --> 35:03.840
I'll quintuple the overtime pay.

35:03.920 --> 35:07.400
If we're shorthanded,
hire more people immediately.

35:17.360 --> 35:20.400
All of our players are very young.

35:21.600 --> 35:23.320
What the heck is this?

35:23.520 --> 35:26.560
Young Master has been modest
about his talents.

35:26.720 --> 35:30.120
He's now displaying a demeanor
very much like you, Mr. Zhen.

35:30.200 --> 35:35.040
Mr. Zhen, you've done a great job
with Young Master. He will go far.

35:40.360 --> 35:41.840
What's your progress?

35:42.480 --> 35:44.600
A great opportunity came up,
and I seized it.

35:44.680 --> 35:47.480
It worked out perfectly. Mr. Zhen...

35:53.880 --> 35:55.000
Nicely done.

35:57.000 --> 35:59.440
But, some of Young Master's ideas

35:59.520 --> 36:01.000
might not be realized in time.

36:04.880 --> 36:07.360
He has plenty of opportunities.

36:07.560 --> 36:09.440
When we get the project,

36:09.560 --> 36:11.840
he'll have all the time in the world
to do it.

36:13.120 --> 36:17.760
But, we can't let him in on the plan.

36:17.920 --> 36:19.320
I don't want to affect his mood.

36:19.720 --> 36:21.000
I understand.

36:21.440 --> 36:22.400
- Let's go.
- After you.

36:30.720 --> 36:33.920
Why isn't Nai back yet? I'm starving!

36:49.040 --> 36:49.880
Mei,

36:50.440 --> 36:51.960
Nai isn't back with my food yet.

36:52.040 --> 36:54.400
I'm starving. Do you have any snacks?

36:54.480 --> 36:56.440
There are nuts in the drawer.
Help yourself.

36:56.520 --> 36:58.080
- Thanks.
- Go ahead.

37:02.880 --> 37:04.240
REAL ESTATE PURCHASE AGREEMENT

37:15.360 --> 37:16.320
What are you up to?

37:20.480 --> 37:21.320
What's this?

37:29.840 --> 37:33.680
Real estate purchase agreement?
Two of them?

37:34.120 --> 37:36.040
Paid off all at once!

37:46.680 --> 37:48.000
What are you doing?

37:53.560 --> 37:54.400
What's this?

37:56.560 --> 37:58.400
It's mine. Give it back.

37:59.880 --> 38:02.120
Come take a look at this calculating boy!

38:02.200 --> 38:04.160
Hao Mei has something to tell us.

38:06.280 --> 38:07.240
What's this?

38:08.680 --> 38:10.480
- Two apartments!
- Two!

38:16.520 --> 38:17.760
Calculating boy,

38:19.000 --> 38:21.800
why didn't you tell me
you went and robbed a bank?

38:22.320 --> 38:23.720
That's right, Mei!

38:23.800 --> 38:25.880
How much lottery prize money
have you got left?

38:26.280 --> 38:27.800
Buy us each a home!

38:28.600 --> 38:30.720
Mei, you're stinking rich,

38:30.800 --> 38:32.840
yet you hide among us the proletariat.

38:32.920 --> 38:33.880
Whatever for?

38:34.480 --> 38:35.920
No!

38:36.520 --> 38:39.680
Brothers, we're now a harmonious society,

38:39.760 --> 38:41.320
where reason is king.

38:41.880 --> 38:45.360
Don't... get violent with me.

38:47.240 --> 38:49.840
K.O.! Help...

38:50.640 --> 38:52.480
Get out of there!

38:55.600 --> 38:58.520
K.O., we're the same class of people.

38:58.600 --> 39:01.040
- You can't oppose the people.
- Right!

39:01.120 --> 39:03.280
- That's right!
- What's this? They're bullying Mr. Girly?

39:04.080 --> 39:05.040
Let's take a look.

39:06.720 --> 39:08.320
Get him out of the way.

39:13.920 --> 39:15.800
Stinky Girly!

39:15.880 --> 39:18.760
How could you do this to me, Hao Mei?

39:18.880 --> 39:19.920
Back in college,

39:20.000 --> 39:22.520
you were stinking rich, yet you borrowed
money from a poor student like me!

39:22.600 --> 39:24.800
You borrowed a lot,
and did you ever repay me?

39:24.880 --> 39:27.920
You think I wanted to do that?
I was really poor!

39:28.000 --> 39:30.520
Back then, I applied for QU
behind my dad's back.

39:31.000 --> 39:32.560
I lived off of 600 RMB a month.

39:32.760 --> 39:35.880
Had I known Capital City had Nai
and sandstorms, I wouldn't have come!

39:35.960 --> 39:37.800
I don't care! Get him!

39:37.880 --> 39:40.720
- Get him!
- Get him!

39:40.800 --> 39:43.400
I'll treat you...

39:44.080 --> 39:45.640
Mr. Hao Mei thinks highly of you.

39:45.720 --> 39:47.840
He compared you to sandstorms.

39:48.200 --> 39:51.840
Give this to Yugong, and tell Hao Mei,
I'll remember that.

40:07.360 --> 40:10.040
NEW UPDATE ON DEMO DATE
FENGTENG TECHNOLOGY

40:41.760 --> 40:45.600
Guys, I discovered
a great hot pot place nearby.

40:45.920 --> 40:48.400
The food's delicious
and reasonably priced.

40:48.480 --> 40:50.920
No way! If we had cheap hot pot,

40:51.000 --> 40:54.080
it'd be an insult to Mei's two apartments.

40:54.320 --> 40:57.480
- Right!
- We must pick the most expensive place!

40:59.720 --> 41:03.760
What would you like to eat, Ms. Weiwei?

41:04.920 --> 41:06.120
Anywhere expensive is fine?

41:08.360 --> 41:11.240
Hey... There's not a kind soul among you.

41:11.920 --> 41:14.000
Let's have seafood. It's the priciest.

41:14.080 --> 41:15.480
It'll easily cost a few grand.

41:15.560 --> 41:18.360
It's perfect for his stinking rich status.

41:19.720 --> 41:22.000
Seafood, it is. How about
the late-night eatery nearby?

41:22.800 --> 41:27.200
You settle too easily! Don't you know
what's posh, classy, and primo?

41:27.280 --> 41:29.080
An eatery is beneath him.

41:29.880 --> 41:31.280
- Don't you agree, Mei?
- So true!

41:31.360 --> 41:32.200
- That's right!
- Yes!

41:36.040 --> 41:38.440
Nai, you're a man of the world.

41:38.520 --> 41:40.400
Pick a place and get a feast out of Mei.

41:40.920 --> 41:43.680
Meeting in the conference room
in five minutes.

44:13.240 --> 44:15.680
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
